  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an antibiotic intervention study to determine the value of using
      piperacillin/tazobactam in reducing the cases of ESBL producing E. coli or K. pneumoniae
      colonization and infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
